{"tid":944822,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"滑雪疑問","createTime":"2018-12-17T12:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T02:47:13.000Z","uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"09c61c74a708891f6f3d110a7e098b8ccc7923b8","tid":944822,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:05:33.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊會滑人生第一次雪 但租裝備上唔太明白<br />\n上網睇見佢有幾樣野收錢 但睇左好多遊記都無點講細節<br />\n<br />\n褸～3000yen<br />\n板～4000yen<br />\n纜車～4000yen<br />\n<br />\n纜車係咪應該一日內任搭？<br />\n租左褸 咁護目鏡手套褲果d係咪包埋？<br />\n板洗唔洗用特定既鞋先扣得實？定佢又包？<br />\n<br />\n如果想跟教練跟班學<br />\n咁仲洗唔洗租以上既野？<br />\n仲有無其他額外收費？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有伸手黨感覺既 我say個sorry先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a21e41ba23a418ff743cb48c2a5b51222b4462a","tid":944822,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5328ee1577bba49516b1bb1bdf525fd13ffa931d","tid":944822,"uid":105059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"通常任搭<br />\n板+鞋一齊租<br />\n衫+褲一齊租<br />\n鏡 盔 手套另買<br />\n教練唔包裝備 除非間舖有package"},{"pid":"551722b07a0bae98edd3f9436eea8909ff570d35","tid":944822,"uid":70832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"我以前手套自己上淘寶買定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n租就滑雪衫褲鞋+板 , 都幾貴, 玩左半日都冇就好L攰"},{"