都要帶雪鏡啦下<br />\n啲雪咁白仲唔好好保護對眼真係雪盲嫁"},{"pid":"f87ab11f7982940593825d4601f107b1f526b16b","tid":944822,"uid":27509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:51:10.000Z","msg":"反而頭盔真係唔係必須，你新手跌到屎忽痛既機會多啲，買個patpat好過"},{"pid":"0455c55834ee4d40cf3440bdc1fbee9da1369533","tid":944822,"uid":130895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658ae8bd9bb4f45375cad44496cc24c300a5fa8f","tid":944822,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a2436fd1c15b81ef56f362a1b333a4a106a5417","tid":944822,"uid":130895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7faac5dcfb864b896a2ce958e2094d183842bc56","tid":944822,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"最煩係頭盔 點放下gip<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T23:32:02.000Z","msg":"租啦，好平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:49:16.000Z","msg":"有得租又唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪乜7都有得租<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"正常係。<br />\n-板，鞋<br />\n-衫，褲<br />\n-頭盔<br />\n-手套<br />\n-眼鏡<br />\n通常咁分，你要咩就租咩"},{"pid":"5516d8de1f5d4f19b0973c4c2d7f85eeea5ead7c","tid":944822,"uid":27509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:55:55.000Z","msg":"仲有預備定對厚長襪<br />\n長襪高過你對鞋<br />\n如果玩snowboard對鞋邊會磨小腿肉"},{"pid":"e2057c9c96d668b98727c07b89315789470ae57f","tid":944822,"uid":130895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"我就因為有帶眼鏡會漸變<br />\n所以得第一日有租鏡，之後覺得無用，之後幾日都無再租。<br />\n頭盔就日日租，因為始終保護個頭。<br />\n聽做滑雪場既朋友講好多意外都係撞到個頭，所以廢時省"},{"pid":"316d589c76079f1503ac23d819c64259831def9f","tid":944822,"uid":135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:03:36.000Z","msg":"上面咪撚9up啦<br />\n goggle 一定要 除非你唔介意盲<br />\n<br />\n通常雪場都有得租<br />\n- Boots<br />\n- Snowboard<br />\n- 衫褲<br />\n<br />\n以下要自備<br />\n- Goggle<br />\n- Pad褲<br />\n- 護膝<br />\n- 護腕<br />\n- 手套<br />\n<br />\n至於頭盔，新手其實速度唔太快，又係新手區其實唔用都ok<br />\n當然有就最好啦<br />\n<br />\n第一次玩唔想投資太多錢可以去迪卡濃或者淘寶"},{"pid":"d6016c61b65f7a65aac8b1eec8c3e3020d08fa86","tid":944822,"uid":130895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:14:42.000Z","msg":"樓上可以未去過滑雪場，得咁少野有得租都講得出<br />\n<br />\n睇樓主長玩定第一次玩<br />\n第一次就全租啦 唔好曬錢<br />\n<br />\n第一次玩仲要舊錢 預去上堂學基本skill<br />\n如果唔係 會好大挫折感"},{"pid":"8ecb21a6336eed7a5de4d8c7d455b15e82798878","tid":944822,"uid":14979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:26:03.000Z","msg":"頭盔、鞋、滑鼠板都有得租<br />\nLift卡就一日內任搭<br />\n<br />\n手套眼鏡就個啲就要自己準備，或者多數個邊有得買但會貴啲，係香港既可以淘寶或者去雅蘭中心最底個間運動舖睇下<br />\n滑雪褸同褲就自己買埋啦，其實揀啲water repellent就得<br />\n滑雪襪有就買埋"},{"pid":"d4198cdb8d8622b9380db48c2e63985c31a4f40f","tid":944822,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:29:49.000Z","msg":"第一次玩真係全租算<br />\n滑雪唔平 有興趣先好買<br />\n頭盔我滑第2次先買 因為比人撞過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dd6f76ecc2916ca97cf2df954d36bbcab356e9","tid":944822,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ee199d45eca78bb1483b82fa27cc226883951e","tid":944822,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"551722b07a0bae98edd3f9436eea8909ff570d35","tid":944822,"uid":70832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"我以前手套自己上淘寶買定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n租就滑雪衫褲鞋+板 , 都幾貴, 玩左半日都冇就好L攰"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"其實係咪唔洗頭盔lol<br />\n<br />\n即係要自備手套同鏡？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"手套，鏡自備"},{"pid":"bcd2f8f987bdf9e30b51b7883159c196eac13630","tid":944822,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"記得買保險"},{"pid":"0a3acf8e3457b4e09baa047ebdfe16246af49224","tid":944822,"uid":68098,"like":0,"di