me":"2018-12-21T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"上堂聽聞都幾爆 最好book定？<br />\n諗緊好唔好上深圳d假雪場學左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5f28e8e313e6482c189c8a103bfc8eaa7b471a","tid":944822,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5da11628c239f9ebb76f1658c36ffe0d28833c27","tid":944822,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"108fd0f8be1e6ca749ad650d7d5188d02174e9ee","tid":944822,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"新手乜都唔識係咪就咁入去雪場都有堂上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"上堂聽聞都幾爆 最好book定？<br />\n諗緊好唔好上深圳d假雪場學左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"咪撚<br />\n硬撚到仆街"},{"pid":"ce8ffd1a9878e442f358e5144bf471b61349cb62","tid":944822,"uid":122458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"黎緊1月去大阪, join左one day tour<br />\n全包 (無食同手套), 包教練1-2小時 ~$1200<br />\n如果你都去大阪 感覺join個團仲方便 又車埋你來回, 租用具入場都成$1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825d2b47a69498e54137397ec689526e4a2467b7","tid":944822,"uid":98797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:57:02.000Z","msg":"簡單啲嚟講就係你凈係著底衫褲去都可以齊到裝滑雪 咩都有得租 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過通常會分開三部分俾你租<br />\n<br />\n滑雪板嗰啲 (ski / snowboard 同鞋)<br />\nwear (雪褲雪衫)<br />\naccessories (眼鏡頭盔手套)<br />\n<br />\n三樣野分開收錢 所以可以自備嗰啲就自己帶啦 慳錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我凈係會租滑雪板 其他全部自己帶 頭盔其實冇乜人戴 通常戴懶帽就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2c5faf2020eeeabf1682b46740e103d723e46b","tid":944822,"uid":165876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ee199d45eca78bb1483b82fa27cc226883951e","tid":944822,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"551722b07a0bae98edd3f9436eea8909ff570d35","tid":944822,"uid":70832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"我以前手套自己上淘寶買定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n租就滑雪衫褲鞋+板 , 都幾貴, 玩左半日都冇就好L攰"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"其實係咪唔洗頭盔lol<br />\n<br />\n即係要自備手套同鏡？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"十分建議租個頭盔<br />\n<br />\n尤其snowboard<br />\n<br />\n好多時急速向後跌， 後腦落地"},{"pid":"4530e38de71b13ece960ae83cd8bd408f477da88","tid":944822,"uid":24556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T21:33:54.000Z","msg":"雪褲入面應該著咩褲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205a788c91a527410d208c31d42f7d4822ae09d1","tid":944822,"uid":227757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T23:38:00.000Z","msg":"褸 如果自己有防水羽絨，其實都唔洗租<br />\n板 就要租，佢會包埋鞋<br />\n纜車 有分好多種票買，睇雪場，你新手上路，唔建議買一日任搭，我第一次滑既時候，係山腳學都學左半日。<br />\n<br />\n護目鏡手套褲，雪場多數拆散黎租，我都係淘寶買。除左護目鏡同手套呢d基本野，極度建議帶冷帽同口罩，你搭纜車上山遇著大風，係凍到入骨。<br />\n<br />\n跟教練學洗唔洗額外收費好睇你去邊個雪場。我之前去北海道星野，係有免費教練，係京都同平昌就要另外俾錢，係法國滑就直頭教練都無"},{"pid":"d5621e447cd68c18c7410a4f8a7a15373b9c6669","tid":944822,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4530e38de71b13ece960ae83cd8bd408f477da88","tid":944822,"uid":24556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T21:33:54.000Z","msg":"雪褲入面應該著咩褲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"長內褲已ok<br />\n加一個護pat<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7CxK5T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7CxK5T.jpg&h=4643b1a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"712e01aa8b6c49d4b13857b51aabbd0b897914df","tid":944822,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"205a788c91a527410d208c31d42f7d4822ae09d1","tid":944822,"uid":227757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r